Road Transport

Sea Freight Services

Sea freight logistics with TrueLog’s expert sea freight services. We offer reliable solutions for international shipping by sea. Discover our comprehensive freight options.
  1. Home

Sea Freight

At TrueLog, we offer a comprehensive suite of sea freight services designed to accommodate a diverse range of cargo types and shipping requirements. Our experienced team ensures the safe and efficient transportation of your goods, providing customized solutions to meet your unique needs.

Email us on

sales@truelog.com.sg

WhatsApp Custom Enquires

+65 9771 8172

Give us a call on

+65 6909 3756

Containerized Services:

  • FCL Secure container space for cargo, maximizing protection and efficiency.
  • LCL Cost-effective consolidation of smaller shipments, optimizing space and reducing costs.
  • Cargo Consolidation Streamlined services for handling multiple shipments, minimizing delays. 1- Dry Bulk Shipping: Specialized transport for bulk commodities or oversized cargo. 2- Roll-on Roll-off (RORO): Efficient transportation solution for vehicles and heavy machinery.
Get a quote

What We Offer

Specialized Solutions

TrueLog provides tailored logistics solutions for complex shipments, ensuring safe and timely delivery worldwide.

Reefer Shipping

Temperature-controlled transport for perishable and pharmaceuticals goods.

Dangerous Cargo Shipping

Expert handling of hazardous materials.

Project Cargo Solutions

Precision handling of complex cargo.

Battery Shipping

We specialize in the safe and compliant transport of batteries, including Lithium and Li-ion batteries used in ICT devices such as laptops and phones, ensuring adherence to all regulatory requirements.

Additional Services:

We also offer services like storage, labeling, packaging, booking, stowage, port handling, stuffing/lashing, customs brokerage, and door-to-door delivery.

Full List of Services: For a detailed list of all our services, please visit More Information.

Connect with Our Experts Today!

Schedule a call, book a meeting, or reach out with your questions—we’re here to help.
Get a Free Consultation
